Class CKR

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CK_RV
      • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CKR

  • public class CKR
extends CK_RV
    Class defining Cryptoki CKR_ constants - Return Value.

    Further information concerning the various return codes is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
